{"tid":1805814,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發]美國宣佈會派出第82空軍師進駐中東 強調不會棄守巴格達大使館","createTime":"2020-01-01T00:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T04:30:38.000Z","uid":133680,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e665b1f682b93ef4970b4bcd20b863a5651a95","tid":1805814,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T00:11:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://trib.al/iMBtxNO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrib.al%2FiMBtxNO&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0aszv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=da842015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://trib.al/iMBtxNO</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SDZMMx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SDZMMx.png&h=5d2f0331&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2741853e283c1a0d3f8a44d8d814547e78d2e75b","tid":1805814,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T00:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srwpaYu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrwpaYu.jpg&h=b38cd696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ec3npyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fec3npyj.jpg&h=648ef6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好唔記得831幫警甴殘殺手足兇手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJzPCRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJzPCRN.jpg&h=f8ccc6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZuNAtv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZuNAtv.png&h=a8f19de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不反都出埋唔好再搵藉口唔出<br />\n1月1號維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n【元旦大遊行　不反已出】<br />\n<br />\n民陣已收到警方發出的不反對通知書，<br />\n可以正式同各位講多次，1.1 維園見！<br />\n<br />\n元旦遊行當日將會有超過 40 個新成立工會同大家見面，歡迎大家瞭解詳情，加入你所屬行業的工會，壯大抗爭的組織力量。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘承諾，並肩同行，五大訴求，缺一不可，<br />\n一月一，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【民陣元旦大遊行】<br />\n2020.1.1 星期三 Wednesday｜2PM<br />\n維園中央草坪 遊行至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to <br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct<br />\n<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲要齊心祝福<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ug7anh2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fug7anh2.png&h=2bf968e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7e143bb980ddc4445b29cef4954af66b307eb55","tid":1805814,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T01:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2795add522c0e2ea3cefa0b3f83dfecae2cbf3","tid":1805814,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:03:01.000Z","msg":"當年西貢都棄守。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ad56d547f5d98ac379da3758add2b3a937d26a","tid":1805814,"uid":282347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:31:50.000Z","msg":"可唔可以派多隊嚟香港幫手驅逐共匪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Sir this way<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58346393ea50fe663b0a4448a346492f2bc7de82","tid":1805814,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96ad56d547f5d98ac379da3758add2b3a937d26a","tid":1805814,"uid":282347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:31:50.000Z","msg":"可唔可以派多隊嚟香港幫手驅逐共匪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Sir this way<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dan